cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.MA 

The paper deals with the problem of reallocation of resources in multi-agent settings, which is a fundamental problem in game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper presents computational hardness results and polynomial-time algorithms, which are typical topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of Pareto optimality, which is a central concept in mechanism design (cs.MA).
